# Anutan constellation, native: Te Kope
msgid "The Bamboo"
msgstr "Der Bambus"

# Description of Anutan constellation The Bamboo
msgid ""
"Bamboo is used to make fishing poles, sailing masts, yards, booms, and "
"outrigger supports."
msgstr ""
"Bambus wird zur Herstellung von Angelruten, Segelmasten, Werften, Auslegern "
"und Auslegerstützen verwendet."

# Anutan constellation, native: Ara Toru
msgid "Path of Three"
msgstr "Pfad der Drei"

# Anutan constellation, native: Manu
msgid "Bird of Flight"
msgstr "Flugvogel"

# Description of Anutan constellation Bird of Flight
msgid "The dominant constellation for Anutans. It can be seen in all seasons."
msgstr ""
"Die dominierende Konstellation für Anutans. Es ist zu allen Jahreszeiten zu "
"sehen."

# Anutan constellation, native: Te Angaanga
msgid "The Tongs"
msgstr "Die Zange"

# Description of Anutan constellation The Tongs
msgid "Used for moving hot stones, coals, and food in an oven."
msgstr ""
"Wird zum Bewegen von heißen Steinen, Kohlen und Speisen in einem Ofen "
"verwendet."

# Anutan constellation, native: Kaavei
msgid "Octopus Tentacle"
msgstr "Octopus Tentakel"

# Anutan constellation, native: Taki Mua
msgid "Forward Precursor"
msgstr "Vorwärts-Vorläufer"

# Anutan constellation, native: Toki
msgid "Adze"
msgstr "Adze"

# Description of Anutan constellation Adze
msgid "Used for cutting canoes and building houses."
msgstr "Wird zum Schneiden von Kanus und zum Bau von Häusern verwendet."

# Anutan constellation, native: Te Aamonga
msgid "The Carrying Stick"
msgstr "Der Tragestock"

# Description of Anutan constellation The Carrying Stick
msgid "Used to carry taro, coconuts, or other food."
msgstr ""
"Wird verwendet, um Taro, Kokosnüsse oder andere Lebensmittel zu "
"transportieren."

# Anutan constellation, native: Te Paka Poi Ika Tapu
msgid "Crevalle-like Fish"
msgstr "Crevalle-ähnlicher Fisch"

# Description of Anutan constellation Crevalle-like Fish
msgid "Marked as uncertain."
msgstr "Als unsicher gekennzeichnet."

# Anutan constellation, native: Taro
msgid "Taro Plant"
msgstr "Taro-Pflanze"

# Anutan constellation, native: Te Kupenga
msgid "The Net"
msgstr "Das Netz"

