msgid "The southernmost of the 3 stars in the muzzle"
msgstr "Der südlichste der drei Sterne in der Schnauze"

msgid "The star in advance of the [above] 3, under the right eye"
msgstr "Der Stern vor den [obigen] drei, unter dem rechten Auge"

