msgid ""
"Stars in the northern fishing-line:  the first in the section beginning at "
"the knot"
msgstr ""
"Sterne in der nördlichen Angelschnur: der erste in dem Abschnitt beginnend "
"am Knoten"

msgid "The southernmost of the 3 stars following after that"
msgstr "Der südlichste der drei ihm folgenden Sterne"

msgid "The northernmost of the 3, which is also on the end of the tail"
msgstr "Der nördlichste der drei, der auch am Schwanzende ist"

